*χρόνος / chronos / khron'-os
*Of uncertain derivation; a space of time (in genitive case, and thus properly distinguished from [[καιρός]] {{GG|2540}}, which designates a fixed or special occasion; and from [[αἰών]] {{GG|165}}, which denotes a particular period) or interval; by extension an individual opportunity; by implication delay: 

=== Noun ===
+ years old, [[season]], [[space]], (X often-) [[time]] (-s), (a) [[while]].

